<org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmi:id="-wZDzQ2mlYPWaogn9jT8P7A" name=",_NeSIANwKEeOYhbmsJkgFpw" guid="-wZDzQ2mlYPWaogn9jT8P7A" changeDate="2014-05-15T10:25:28.677+0200">
  <mainDescription>The idea is to improve customer satisfaction, optimise the view of the organisation from the outside, and use this&#xD;
mechanism as a platform on which to identify new business opportunities.</mainDescription>
  <sections xmi:id="_qT62kNwKEeOYhbmsJkgFpw" name="Define the Physical Structure" guid="_qT62kNwKEeOYhbmsJkgFpw">
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    It is important to define the best structure for this mechanism and this selection depends on the service needs&#xD;
    (global, local, 24/7, etc.).&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Taken into account the SaaS business model the best structure for the helpdesk is the virtual one. The main aim of a&#xD;
    virtual service is to utilize the advantages of both centralized and distributed service desks. In a virtual&#xD;
    communication mechanism:&lt;br />&#xD;
    • Knowledge is centralised.&lt;br />&#xD;
    • Unnecessary duplication is avoided, with the consequent cost savings.&lt;br />&#xD;
    • A &quot;local service&quot; can be offered without incurring extra costs.&lt;br />&#xD;
    • The quality of service is uniform and consistent.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_5sJk0NwKEeOYhbmsJkgFpw" name="Define a Logical Structure" guid="_5sJk0NwKEeOYhbmsJkgFpw">
    <sectionDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The definition of this Logical structure for comunication mechanish is to ensure the following aspects:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    - People should be&amp;nbsp;familiar with the protocols for interaction with users: scripts, checklists, etc.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    - People&amp;nbsp;should be&amp;nbsp;equipped with software tools they need to log their interactions with users.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    - People&amp;nbsp;should&amp;nbsp;know when to escalate incidents to higher levels or contribute to discussions on the&#xD;
    compliance with SLAs.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    - People&amp;nbsp;should receive training on the company's products and services.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;/p></sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The purpose is to define an appropriate physical and logical structure that enables to create a communication mechanism&#xD;
    whose objectives are aligned with the business processes.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
